<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="disappoint-vt">disappoint <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌdɪsə'pɔɪnt/    美 /ˌdɪsə'pɔɪnt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使失望：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>disappoint sb’s expectations</strong>
辜负某人的期望</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m sorry to disappoint you, but I can’t come after all.
真抱歉让你失望，可我实在不能来。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>disappointing /ˌdɪsə'pɔɪntɪŋ/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a disappointing exam result
令人失望的考试成绩</p></div></div>